  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/1a828cb7b2a99a5432b7e93f74c29390.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've just inherited your Grandpa's quaint typewriter store... but, there's a twist: you need to revamp this business for the modern world through custom keyboard designing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/da02424ddede793295244ae5a7da707f.avif?t=1766398537\" width=618 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's now your job to turn boards into coins. Design the keyboard of your dreams down to the individual key; apply skins, swap to custom key caps, mix in symbols, perfect your lighting & challenge your imagination. Can you earn enough coins, manage your stock and unlock the best from the Capslock Catalogue?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/7ed9315a0cfbd14bb86efdd89ba379cc.avif?t=1766398537\" width=618 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/d74a5f853e915b1a70ed801cf276327c.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capslock is a casual game focused on design and testing your imagination. Choose between 130+ skins, 260+ custom keys, 270+ symbols and more to test your designs and make unique keyboards. Relax as you listen to the 'clicky' sounds to help you unwind and immerse into a keyboard building environment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start from scratch - solve the puzzle of dragging and dropping each key into its' slot to build out your keyboard, or dive straight into designing and auto-fill all your keys with the press of a button! You can edit one key at a time, or make changes to your whole board - Capslock moves at a pace which suits you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/da02424ddede793295244ae5a7da707f.avif?t=1766398537\" width=618 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/b4bbc543d6d6c2ab87662920d539cce8.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capslock is a stock based game! The more boards you sell, the more coins you will have to explore the <i>\"Capslock Catalogue\"</i>. You will need to keep an eye on your stock levels and purchases to ensure your business stays profitable and you have access to the best content ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/cc8317e546d539e7688c82f89a1e2eaf.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many features, big and small, to ensure complete freedom in designing a keyboard. Tweak each keys lighting or have fun with various RGB sequences. Rotate keys, write out your text, change keyboard & background colours or try your designs out on multiple boards! Capslock is the tool to create your dream boards.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/853ad892e2a1abf399adfc7970275051.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Capslock is our first release from an indie team - it is our dream to create a keyboard designer community and listen to our players to enhance the game as it develops !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/173f0b896da34240e8dbbebea04571c5.poster.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/173f0b896da34240e8dbbebea04571c5.webm?t=1766398537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/173f0b896da34240e8dbbebea04571c5.mp4?t=1766398537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/a1a42bdf34df8fc7b5e5a905d9dcd9b7.avif?t=1766398537\" width=618 height=100 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/1a828cb7b2a99a5432b7e93f74c29390.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've just inherited your Grandpa's quaint typewriter store... but, there's a twist: you need to revamp this business for the modern world through custom keyboard designing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/da02424ddede793295244ae5a7da707f.avif?t=1766398537\" width=618 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's now your job to turn boards into coins. Design the keyboard of your dreams down to the individual key; apply skins, swap to custom key caps, mix in symbols, perfect your lighting & challenge your imagination. Can you earn enough coins, manage your stock and unlock the best from the Capslock Catalogue?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/7ed9315a0cfbd14bb86efdd89ba379cc.avif?t=1766398537\" width=618 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/d74a5f853e915b1a70ed801cf276327c.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capslock is a casual game focused on design and testing your imagination. Choose between 130+ skins, 260+ custom keys, 270+ symbols and more to test your designs and make unique keyboards. Relax as you listen to the 'clicky' sounds to help you unwind and immerse into a keyboard building environment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start from scratch - solve the puzzle of dragging and dropping each key into its' slot to build out your keyboard, or dive straight into designing and auto-fill all your keys with the press of a button! You can edit one key at a time, or make changes to your whole board - Capslock moves at a pace which suits you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/da02424ddede793295244ae5a7da707f.avif?t=1766398537\" width=618 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/b4bbc543d6d6c2ab87662920d539cce8.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capslock is a stock based game! The more boards you sell, the more coins you will have to explore the <i>\"Capslock Catalogue\"</i>. You will need to keep an eye on your stock levels and purchases to ensure your business stays profitable and you have access to the best content ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/cc8317e546d539e7688c82f89a1e2eaf.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many features, big and small, to ensure complete freedom in designing a keyboard. Tweak each keys lighting or have fun with various RGB sequences. Rotate keys, write out your text, change keyboard & background colours or try your designs out on multiple boards! Capslock is the tool to create your dream boards.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/853ad892e2a1abf399adfc7970275051.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Capslock is our first release from an indie team - it is our dream to create a keyboard designer community and listen to our players to enhance the game as it develops !</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/173f0b896da34240e8dbbebea04571c5.poster.avif?t=1766398537\" width=616 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/173f0b896da34240e8dbbebea04571c5.webm?t=1766398537\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/173f0b896da34240e8dbbebea04571c5.mp4?t=1766398537\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2931790/extras/a1a42bdf34df8fc7b5e5a905d9dcd9b7.avif?t=1766398537\" width=618 height=100 /></span></p>",
